RIGHT EXCELLENT HONORABLE MARCUS GARVEY 134TH SOLAR RETURN TOUR……..

Dr.Umar Returns to Denver(CO): Friday August 13th@5pm(3-9pm), “Black Parent Advocate Book Release: Marcus Garvey & the Black Independence Movement” 5080 Paris Street 80239, iamculture@gmail.com, drumarjohnson@yahoo.com, 844-4DR-UMAR

B)Dr.Umar Returns to Louisville(KY): Saturday August 14th@3pm(11am-5pm), “Most Honorable Marcus Mosiah Garvey 134th Earthday Celebration” Kentucky Center for Afrikan American Heritage, 1701 W. Muhummad Ali Blvd 40203, 502-873-6301, SelfEsteemInc.Org, 844-4DR-UMAR

C)Dr.Umar Returns to Macon(GA): Sunday August 15th@5pm(2pm-8pm), “Honorable Marcus Garvey 134th Earthday Celebration” Homeland Village Cultural Center, 2910 Napier Avenue 31204, 706.623.2365, DrUmarMacon@Gmail.com, no registration or tickets necessary, 844-4DR-UMAR, drumarjohnson.com 

D) Dr.Umar in Harlem(NY): Tuesday August 17th@8pm(7-10pm), “Honorable Marcus Mosiah Garvey 134th Earthday Tribute” Metropolitan Baptist Church, 151 W. 128th Street at corner of Adam Clayton Powell Jr Blvd, 929-624-4142, buyblackcampaign7@gmail.com, drumarjohnson.com

node.text: “Dr. Johnson, I wanted to VERIFY first and make sure this was you before I went into any detail on anything.. But I'll start here... I'm sure you hear this a lot, and maybe NOT ENOUGH, but THANK YOU!!! For allllll you've done and what you continue to do for African children and families... It's takes a realllllll one to put their contact info out to the world and make them self available to the people...I just wanna encourage you, to NOT STOP... The times that you may get discouraged, or feel like you're fighting allllll by yourself,,,,,,KNOW,,,, that after you've been TRIED WITH THE FIRE, you WILL COME OUT, as PURE GOLD..... The calling on your life is DIVINE DESTINY, and I'll Tell you like I tell my BIG 10yr old son...GOD gave you, your size for a REASON, you were BUILT with the size of  a warrior of GOD!!!Because GOD KNEW the giants you'd face... You are CALLED to the NATIONS!!!! CONTINUE to WALK,, in your ancestors steps, CONTINUE to LEAD,,,, with BOLDNESS and COURAGE....CONTINUE to TEACH,,,, Because when YOU SPEAK,,,,NATIONS LISTEN!!! Even the ones that don't wanna hear or BELIEVE what you say,  THEY LISTEN...Because the TRUTH, gets our ATTENTION one way or another...So, my brother,  KEEP your head to the sky, and ALWAYS KNOW,  that THIS ,,, is YOUR PURPOSE and CAN'T NOBODY,,,,, AIN'T NOBODY,,, and WON'T NOBODY,  do what YOU DO!!! THANK YOU AGAIN,  and be BLESSED....”
